<li><strong>Trezor Model T (Price: $169)</strong> &#8211; The Trezor Model T is another reliable hardware wallet option. It provides advanced security features and supports XRP transactions. While it&#8217;s more expensive than the Ledger Nano S, the Trezor Model T offers a larger touchscreen display and a sleek design.</li>



<li><strong>KeepKey (Price: $79)</strong> &#8211; KeepKey is a hardware wallet that offers a simple and secure way to manage your Ripple wallet. It has a premium design and supports XRP transactions. With its mid-range price, KeepKey provides a good balance between price and functionality.</li>
</ol>



