<li>They&#8217;re resistant to hacking and online threats, providing an extra layer of security for your Ripple holdings.</li>



<li>Physical coins are easy to transport and can be stored in a safe or vault, ensuring the safety of your assets.</li>



<li>They&#8217;re a great option for those who prefer a physical representation of their cryptocurrency holdings.</li>



<li>Physical coins can also serve as a collector&#8217;s item, adding value and uniqueness to your Ripple storage solution.</li>
</ul>



<p>With physical coins, you can have the best of both worlds &#8211; the security of offline storage and the convenience of owning a physical representation of your Ripple assets.</p>



